{"tid":1385870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【致】【抗】【爭】【者】","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:33:05.000Z","uid":213379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62fa0c5d4d5a3438fa75a4a6b91993f75f97576d","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"借朋友帳戶代出文, 出文者同為抗爭者。<br />\nPS. 如果有共嗚, 請推比 學聯/民陣/泛民主派等身邊所有抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拋頭顱 灑熱血</strong></span><br />\n經過一個多月的抗爭日子, 香港人已經發揮得淋漓盡致。<br />\n由文宣輿論 到 遊行衝擊, 雙管齊下, 引起各界迴響同為史無前例。<br />\n過程一點一滴, 不再一一細算, <strong>在此小弟向各位既付出致出衷心敬意</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時有一點小弟想表達, 希望各位有<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">更深一層覺悟</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要!升!級!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>前線, 物資, 支援, 和理非都要做!!</strong><br />\n抗爭運動到今日, 自覺開始進入膠著狀態, <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>抗爭變得愈來愈平常及生活化</strong></span>。<br />\n政府都唔再理你, 因為彼此<strong>已經習慣左個模式</strong>。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因此必須全力支持8月5日罷工運動!!! 炮轟政府!!!</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">癱你老母交通! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷你老母工!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n先引用天琦一番說話<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">【政治工作不只要令支持自己的人，繼續支持自己，<br />\n更要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法。】</span><br />\n<br />\n大家必需要了解, 抗爭者的確佔香港一大勢力。<br />\n但會作出實際行動的, 可能<strong>只是勢力的其中一部分</strong>。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因此抗爭者, 必須了解及珍惜8月5日罷工的重要性!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果成功令大部分市民不能上班, 罷工先係<span style=\"color: red;\">直接攻擊政府經濟!!</span><br />\n<br />\n方法/行動/言語等等唔多講<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以令到8月5所有人返唔到工, 唔洗教喇掛?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有眼前路，沒有身後身。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n買一張車票, 08:00 去大既中轉站, 光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5日, 我要你地既幫手, OK?</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ab05ebb5f8c972294f7b5e4884c31bd818578735","tid":1385870,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8963a09fc5eb4b17a19971dd687b64557779125","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:48:15.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n1次"},{"pid":"dd3951e6a8a832ba2de1302684df0261bd831cfa","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n2次"},{"pid":"d75b505814b9cf3647bee6b3c18fe7d0129b2b8e","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n3次"},{"pid":"289936517f841eca5e8bc36094f9943855086ad0","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:48:48.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n4次"},{"pid":"6bb197d7cef5809aab20c3b06abf139ff36b3bf5","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n5次"},{"pid":"c3ea89b112724d38b3deba7d3b75c9f196f79d5f","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n6次"},{"pid":"2bbf67589186a558c58cde773a915c852cd87358","tid":1385870,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"自推十次, 覺唔覺醒到真係睇依鋪<br />\n7次"},{"pid":"77c04ba02813c2672ade84